				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Arka has just killed Sazza with her crossbow. Reaction of the party.\r\n\r\nRequires 2 characters.\r\n\r\nSpeaker 1 is the character who let Arka do the deed through the dialog, as such their reply should keep that in mind.\r\n\r\nSpeaker 2 is a nearby companion who instigates the PAD and can have an opinionated line."
